### Installation

> **Note**: This is an experimental Zig SDK for OpenFGA. Zig support in OpenAPI Generator is not yet available, so this SDK uses the C client generator as a base with Zig-specific adaptations.

To use this SDK in your Zig project, you can reference it in your `build.zig.zon`:

```zig
.dependencies = .{
    .openfga = .{
        .url = "{{gitHost}}/{{gitUserId}}/{{gitRepoId}}/archive/refs/tags/v{{packageVersion}}.tar.gz",
    },
},
```

Then in your `build.zig`:

```zig
const openfga = b.dependency("openfga", .{
    .target = target,
    .optimize = optimize,
});
exe.root_module.addImport("openfga", openfga.module("openfga"));
```
